Subject: tests: Create a temporary XDG_CONFIG_HOME

XDG_CONFIG_DIR is not part of the basedirs spec. Use XDG_CONFIG_HOME
instead, which is probably what was intended.

Signed-off-by: Simon McVittie <smcv@debian.org>
Forwarded: https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/mutter/-/merge_requests/4012
